{"tid":2111621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戴耀廷：初選已完成 下一步是選舉前民調 之後將專注學術工作","createTime":"2020-07-16T15:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T17:06:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f41a98cff60ad0c5c17ab5069161b79c3421e70f","tid":2111621,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:59:22.000Z","msg":"隨著初選投票完成，各區都產生了出選隊伍，民主派35＋初選協調的主要工作已完成。接著就要由各區的出選隊伍同心合力為達目標而努力。<br />\n<br />\n當前的挑戰是多少勝出隊伍能成功入閘，及 Plan B 部署能否成功應對選舉主任的無理DQ。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"red\">接著是在選舉日前兩周會開始進行民調，結果會在 9 月2 日公布。一些區的參選團隊會按民調結果停止選舉工程，讓選民清楚知道民主派在各區最後的候選名單是哪幾隊。</span></span></span></strong><br />\n最後一步，就要靠近二百萬名選民，自主、策略及聰明地把選票平均分配到各區的候選名單，由所有人一起來完成這看似是不可能的任務。<br />\n<br />\n作為民主派 35＋初選的協調者，到了這階段，餘下需要做的已不多。見到61萬人自發地參與了初選的投票，足證過去幾個月的努力，是非常值得。<br />\n<br />\n因過去幾個月的勞累，我希望在未來的一段日子，爭取多一些休息時間，也可以更專注於學術的工作。<br />\n當然，我不是甚麼也不再做，我必會與所有認同民主普選的香港人走在一起，在各自的位置，為達成這目標，繼續努力，直至民主普選臨到香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/270507093143059/posts/1445464608980629/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F270507093143059%2Fposts%2F1445464608980629%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=8aa968d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/270507093143059/posts/1445464608980629/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"8bed06f050c58a9804901050311397c22d6e159f","tid":2111621,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038ae37aa0aedb4ca8cec045ddd8397ae1d64fd8","tid":2111621,"uid":202296,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T17:00:26.000Z","msg":"吓<br />\n原來佢地唔研究點配票架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbut respect"},{"pid":"8b08baa5d5a1129d25ac7f54eff8296151a954ac","tid":2111621,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"咁早就講定會淡出 係唔係有啲咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cbbdb7cf1cc53d45909f528d3a5927df5543bf9","tid":2111621,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T17:03:31.000Z","msg":"選都未選就講以後 早唔早啲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d2cb45f339fd4a62e6b2a232cba1e5642a2d05","tid":2111621,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"點配票呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"6a985c17f9c1078b91f39eae42cb663c85b526ed","tid":2111621,"uid":276440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4d2cb45f339fd4a62e6b2a232cba1e5642a2d05","tid":2111621,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"點配票呀屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"最後一步，就要靠近二百萬名選民，自主、策略及聰明地把選票平均分配到各區的候選名單，由所有人一起來完成這看似是不可能的任務。<br />\n<br />\n-------------------<br />\n講咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}